Topics Covered : React Hooks , React Router DOM , React Event Systems.
1. Create a Book Store application with necessary navigations.
Home page should consists of login and signup option 

Once the user sign’s up the route should be automatically navigated to the login page (use Events for required field’s validations)

Once the user login is successful, show the dashboard with user details with his profile information, delivery address, wish list, and recently purchased items.  (Can be static)

Once the user clicks proceed to shopping,

Show the products page where the user can view the books, and provide the following features.

Display books in no specific order when the component is loaded
Search book by author
Sort Books by price
Sort Books by rating

Note: Proper layouts, coding standards and code splitting will be evaluated.
